text: Zhané (pronounced jah-nay) was an American R&B-soul; group. The group was known for several major songs, like "Groove Thang", "Hey Mr DJ" and "Sending My Love". The group was part of Queen Latifah's Flavor Unit collective. The group broke up during the late 1990s.
